        "Dear Jane,",
        "I am writing this mail to express my gratitude to you for your help related to my presentation conducted yesterday.",
        "I finally finished my presentation yesterday, which was a resounding success. It was highly acclaimed by my boss and colleagues in my department. With the aid of the book you lent, I could explain the pros and cons of social media precisely. Having a clear understanding of social media was essential for all the members in my department because our job is to set up marketing strategies through a diversity of channels.",
